DREAM: LPS vs unstim

#128 samples LPS from 62 donors vs 135 unstim from 61 donors #form <- ~ stimulation + (1|donor_id) + age + picard_pct_ribosomal_bases + region + picard_pct_mrna_bases + sex + picard_pct_percent_duplication + picard_pct_pf_reads_aligned

load("~/MiGASti/genes_counts_cultured.Rdata")
load("~/MiGASti/docs/res_DREAM_LPS.Rdata")
load("~/MiGASti/docs/res_DREAM_IFNy.Rdata")
load("~/MiGASti/docs/res_DREAM_R848.Rdata")
load("~/MiGASti/docs/res_DREAM_ATP.Rdata")
load("~/MiGASti/docs/res_DREAM_TNFa.Rdata")
load("~/MiGASti/docs/res_DREAM_IL4.Rdata")
load("~/MiGASti/docs/res_DREAM_DEX.Rdata")

FDR < 0.05 LPS vs unstim

length(which(res_dreamLPS$adj.P.Val<0.05))
## [1] 6270

FDR distribution LPS vs unstim

res = res_dreamLPS
p = ggplot(res, aes(P.Value))
p + geom_density(color="darkblue", fill="lightblue") +   theme_classic() + ggtitle("FDR Distribution")

Fold Change Distribution LPS vs unstim

p = ggplot(res, aes(logFC))
p + geom_density(color = "darkblue", fill = "lightblue") + theme_classic() + ggtitle("Fold Change Distribution")

MA plot LPS vs unstim

plot.data = res
data = data.frame(plot.data)
data$P.Value = -log10(data$P.Value)
data$fifteen = as.factor(abs(data$adj.P.Val < 0.05))
ma = ggplot(data, aes(AveExpr, logFC, color = fifteen))
ma + geom_point() +
  scale_color_manual(values = c("black", "red"), labels = c ("> 0.05", "< 0.05")) +
  labs(title = "MA plot", color = "labels") +
  theme_classic()

  #theme(plot.title = element_text(hjust = 0.5)) + ylim (-10,10) + xlim(-4,22)

Volcano plot LPS vs unstim

vp = ggplot(data, aes(logFC, P.Value, color = fifteen))
vp + geom_point() +
  scale_color_manual(values = c("black", "red"), labels = c("> 0.05", "< 0.05")) + 
  labs(title = "Gene Level Volcano Plot", color = "FDR") +
  #theme(plot.title = element_text(hjust = 0.5)) +
  theme_classic() +
  xlim(-10,10) + ylim(0, 20) + ylab("-log10 pvalue")
## Warning: Removed 119 rows containing missing values (geom_point).
